---
// src/pages/aboutme.astro

import '../../styles/global.css';
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About Me">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
    <!-- LEFT: Title and Text -->
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight font-serif">
        Who am I
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg pb-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        I am incessantly curious, guided by mystery and beauty. Fascinated by the Renaissance man concept, I constantly aspire toward becoming one. As an idealist, I seek Aret and wish to make the Universe a more fun place for all beings. I want to adventure in the most interesting way for me in this game.

      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-primary">Technologies I use:</span> HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Astro, Tailwind CSS, Python, VPS, Linux, AI integrations, PostgreSQL.
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-primary">My Zones of Genius (possibly, it's too soon to have much confidence):</span>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-1">
            <li>Deep Research</li>
            <li>Nexalism</li>
            <li>Strategic/Systematic Thinking</li>
            <li>Metatheory</li>
            <li>Beauty + Intellectual</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-primary">My top 12 personal values (not in order):</span> 
            <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-1">
              <li>Intelligence</li>
              <li>Knowledge</li>
              <li>Beauty</li>
              <li>Criticality</li>
              <li>Fun</li>
              <li>Deep Connections
                <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
                  <li>Living beings and Ideas</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>Authenticity</li>
              <li>Idealism</li>
              <li>Evolution
                <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
                  <li>Arete</li>
                  <li>Antifragility</li>
                  <li>Life</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>Honor
                <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
                  <li>Loyalty/Commitment for what is meaningful to me</li>
                  <li>Coherence / Integrity</li> 
                </ul>  
              </li>
              <li>The Good</li>
              <li>Legacy</li>  
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-primary">Things I love:</span> Chamomile tea in a pretty cup.
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-primary">Things I avoid:</span> Beans under the rice.
        </div>
        <!-- Quotes
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-primary">Gotta:</span>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-1 space-y-1 italic">
            <li>"The universe is relation."</li>
            <li>"Knowledge becomes meaningful through its impact."</li>
            <li>"Beauty isn't mere decoration—it's foundational structure."</li>
            <li>"Live deliberately; embody Areté."</li>
          </ul>
        </div> 
        -->
        
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Profile image -->
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <img src="/about-me/cat.png" alt="Rhyan's Portrait" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg max-h-[500px] object-cover" />
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
